    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Salminus iquitensis, living specimens: (A) Peru, Ucayali, río Aguaytia; (B) ROM 93073, Ecuador, Paztaza, río Bobonaza; (C) CZUT-IC 7147, 133.6 mm SL: Colombia, Guaviare, Río Guayabero basin; (D) IAvH-P 17096, Colombia, Meta, Río Guayabero. Photo A by A. Linares, B by N.K. Lujan, C by A. Urbano-Bonilla, D by Mark Sabaj." ;
